item.dc:creator: Ike
item.title: News :: ECL, SC and GOTS
item.description:
The European Club League is now entering its final phase, and many players still have the chance to win this title. Please make sure you get all your games played until September 25th. Players with less than 20 games should get playing asap if they want to keep their team.

Things are also heating up in the Summer Challenge '06 with Atol to meet either sheepshagger or gecko14 in the final. Will gecko14 walk away with his first tournament title after three ladder wins?

Finally, you have decided that cycobbs has won the Season 18 GOTS Competition with this beautiful Henry/Bergkamp combination. Well done!
